org.littleshoot.proxy.impl

Class DefaultHttpProxyServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.littleshoot.proxy.impl.DefaultHttpProxyServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpProxyServer

    public class DefaultHttpProxyServer
extends Object
implements HttpProxyServer

    Primary implementation of an HttpProxyServer.

    DefaultHttpProxyServer is bootstrapped by calling bootstrap() or bootstrapFromFile(String), and then calling DefaultHttpProxyServerBootstrap#start() or DefaultHttpProxyServerBootstrap#start(boolean, boolean). For example: 

     DefaultHttpProxyServer server =
         DefaultHttpProxyServer
                 .bootstrap()
                 .withPort(8090)
                 .start();
